available properties."],[1,[],0,8]]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"However, different systems might represent these fields in different ways. Perhaps we only store the total seats available and the number of seats sold."],[1,[],0,9]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"Enter Taxi expressions, stage left."],[1,[],0,10]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"Given our two base properties:"],[1,[],0,11]]],[10,0],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"We can then express the relationship between these two fields using a Taxi expression:"]]],[10,1],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"As a result, if we’re querying this data through Vyne, all our consumers have to do is ask for the data they need and Vyne will apply the expression in order to create that field from the data available in the source system."],[1,[],0,12]]],[10,2],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"We get a number of benefits from doing this:"]]],[3,"ul",[[[0,[1],1,"Cleaner code"],[0,[],0," - Our code isn’t littered with transformation logic. We can request the data we want from the data layer and immediately apply the logic which is core to the consuming service"]],[[0,[1],1,"Flexibility "],[0,[],0,"- If our consuming service isn’t flexible (e.g. it’s a legacy system, or cost of change is high.) then we can immediately reshape the data without needed to make a change to the producing system"]],[[0,[1],1,"Observability & Lineage "],[0,[],0,"- By representing transformations in the data layer, we can clearly track how systems are manipulating data and how it’s flowing through our systems end to end. This is otherwise known as data lineage and there’s a number of ways Vyne "],[0,[2],1,"makes this visible"],[0,[],0,". The alternative is that this logic is obscured in the code of the consuming system."],[1,[],0,13]]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"This works equally well with operations on other types such as Dates and Booleans, and other arithmetic operations such as greater than, less than, and equality conditions. "],[1,[],0,14]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"It’s also just one of a number of features in Taxi that let query writers express how they want to receive data more accurately."],[1,[],0,15]]],[1,"p",[[0,[],0,"Check it out at "],[0,[3],1,"taxilang.org"]]],[1,"p",[[1,[],0,16]]]]}
